---
import Shell from '../layouts/Shell.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---
<Shell title="Refund Policy · DigitalChiselCo" description="DigitalChiselCo 14-day refund and cancellation policy for digital STL file purchases, in line with Paddle's Buyer Terms.">
  <Breadcrumbs crumbs={[{ label: 'Refund Policy' }]} />

  <article class="prose prose-sm max-w-3xl text-ink-700">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl text-bronze-800 mb-6">Refund Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-ink-700/50 mb-8">Last updated: July 6, 2026</p>

    <p>We want you to be completely happy with your purchase. Checkout and payments are handled by our Merchant of Record, <strong>Paddle.com Market Ltd</strong>, and this policy follows <a href="https://www.paddle.com/legal/checkout-buyer-terms" class="text-bronze-600" rel="nofollow">Paddle's Buyer Terms</a>.</p>

    <h2>1. 14-Day Right to Cancel &amp; Full Refund</h2>
    <p>You may <strong>cancel your purchase and request a full refund within 14 days</strong> of the date of purchase, for any reason. You do not need to give a reason — if you contact us within 14 days, we will process your refund.</p>
    <p>Because our products are digital downloads, once a refund is issued your licence to use the downloaded file(s) ends, and you agree to delete any copies you have downloaded.</p>

    <h2>2. How to Request a Refund</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:jolly@digitalchiselco.com" class="text-bronze-600">jolly@digitalchiselco.com</a> within <strong>14 days</strong> of purchase — or contact Paddle directly using the receipt they emailed you.</li>
      <li>Include your <strong>order number</strong> (or the email used at checkout).</li>
      <li>We will review and process your refund promptly, typically within <strong>2 business days</strong>.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>3. Membership Plans</h2>
    <p>Membership plans are one-time payments and are covered by the same <strong>14-day refund right</strong> described above.</p>

    <h2>4. Refund Method &amp; Timing</h2>
    <p>Approved refunds are processed by <strong>Paddle.com Market Ltd</strong> back to your original payment method. Depending on your bank or card issuer, it may take <strong>5–10 business days</strong> to appear on your statement. Paddle will email you confirmation once the refund has been issued.</p>

    <h2>5. Chargebacks</h2>
    <p>If anything is wrong with your order, please contact us first. We honour the 14-day refund above and can almost always resolve issues faster directly than through a bank chargeback.</p>

    <h2>6. Contact</h2>
    <p>Need help? Reach us at <a href="mailto:jolly@digitalchiselco.com" class="text-bronze-600">jolly@digitalchiselco.com</a> or use the <a href="/contact" class="text-bronze-600">contact page</a>. A real person reads every message.</p>
  </article>
</Shell>
